{"type": "article", "id": 25917, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-25T06:59:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26676, "name": "Niloo"}, {"id": 26677, "name": "Time Maze"}, {"id": 26678, "name": "3tubes"}, {"id": 16959, "name": "Charles Kalpakian"}, {"id": 26679, "name": "Livi"}, {"id": 26680, "name": "Dog Den"}, {"id": 26681, "name": "Razy2 Design Group"}, {"id": 26682, "name": "Dargett Brewery"}, {"id": 26683, "name": "Braind"}, {"id": 26684, "name": "Khodi Feiz"}, {"id": 746, "name": "Daniel Libeskind"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145456A3FOPqZm1tJIU2dC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Niloo by Khodi Feiz</h2>\n<p class=\"\">设计师 <a href=\"http://api.viglink.com/api/click?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_146148405339211&amp;key=6ab1d62aaf9dbafae96546ba3ca1b2ac&amp;libId=ine9vbgj0100x1tt000DLnhlqhdxv&amp;loc=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Fniloo-artifort-khodi-feiz%2F&amp;v=1&amp;out=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.feizdesign.com%2F&amp;ref=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Fniloo-artifort-khodi-feiz%2Fkhodi_feiz_artifort_niloo_chair_9%2F&amp;title=Niloo%20for%20Artifort%20by%20Khodi%20Feiz%20-%20Design%20Milk&amp;txt=Khodi%20Feiz\">Khodi Feiz</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.artifort.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Artifort</a> 所设计的这款 <a href=\"http://api.viglink.com/api/click?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_146148381948314&amp;key=6ab1d62aaf9dbafae96546ba3ca1b2ac&amp;libId=ine9mwhx0100x1tt000DApzl8q5wiz9gr&amp;loc=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Fniloo-artifort-khodi-feiz%2F&amp;v=1&amp;out=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.artifort.com%2Fcollection%2Fmodel%2Fdetail%2Farmchairs_niloo&amp;title=Niloo%20for%20Artifort%20by%20Khodi%20Feiz%20-%20Design%20Milk&amp;txt=Niloo\">Niloo</a> 椅由两个拼接在一起的软垫所组成，设计的原型来自非洲刚果地区的同样由两部分组成的椅子。穿过弧形椅背上的插槽，座位的另一部分在椅背后成为了椅子的另一个支脚，兼具了美观和实用性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181656vm6k1y9PwhBSzZNW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181657NkKL7tdTobEF13CY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181657jWwJKRc40MiBSbOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181658JzCnHh65xeobLRdj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181658JVgRknPwb5s6D2uN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Time Maze clock by Daniel Libeskind</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这个名为时间迷宫（<a href=\"http://api.viglink.com/api/click?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_146148520070416&amp;key=6ab1d62aaf9dbafae96546ba3ca1b2ac&amp;libId=ineagxra0100x1tt000DLvqeblqywj2p5&amp;loc=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Ftime-maze-clock-daniel-libeskind-alessi%2F&amp;v=1&amp;out=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alessi.com%2Fen%2Fproducts%2Fdetail%2Fdl01-time-maze-wall-clock&amp;title=Time%20Maze%20Clock%20by%20Daniel%20Libeskind%20for%20Alessi%20-%20Design%20Milk&amp;txt=Time%20Maze\">Time Maze</a>）的挂钟由建筑师 <a href=\"http://libeskind.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Daniel Libeskind</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.alessi.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">Alessi</a> 所设计。通过奇异的线条组合，时间“既非线形或圆形，而是一个有着抽象联系和趣味互动的迷宫”这一概念得到了充分的体现。整个挂钟由不锈钢制成，红色部分为钟面，12 个小圆点代表了刻度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181659rCfjcEU25sNDpoXx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181659Ef73jXU8C2gcaS9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181700ZN327IGo0cnqaSke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>3tubes by charles kalpakian</h2>\n<p class=\"\">黎巴嫩的 <a href=\"https://www.bespoke-edition.com/eu/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">charles kalpakian</a> 工作室在推出了 2tubes 照明系统之后，在产品线中又加入了这款由三根金属管子组成的吊灯。设计灵感来源于 x、y、z 三根轴线，纯白和金属细管以不对称的方式组合在一起，简洁又独特。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181700yhoRDMm62pb9cTWk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13691932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181701Fwfvlnckzqh7yYQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82885086\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181701P5wuhV9eOdDga248.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71882641\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181702MTJWVoaKEqkUszlA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46332518\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181702dTPpveKlnN7SQgsr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Livi by Livi team</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这个多用途的可粘壁花盆名叫 <a href=\"http://creodes.com/\">Livi</a>，由一个来自美国旧金山的设计团队打造，小巧的设计很容易让人联想到壁虎。花盆有四个支脚，底部采用了纳米微吸胶技术，可以重复粘贴在任何表面，而且不会留下痕迹。如果你参与众筹，单只的早鸟价为 12 美元。你可以在它的 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1982070287/livi-a-new-way-to-experience-plants\">Kickstarter</a> 页面上看到更多的相关信息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181703QS93bKiI8405CxJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181703bmTFVZE5Q0YhKPA8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37113402\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181704O8Y34j6sy7PtFAXL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181705lKW9EXtux8Ln1wyk.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181706qZ28HxNUWIBSorOF.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56029412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Dog Den by Razy2 Design Group</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这个名叫 Dog Den 的宠物小床是 <a href=\"http://razy2.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://razy2.com/', 'Razy2 Design Group');\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Razy2 Design Group</a> 为波兰家具装饰品牌 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mnomodesign/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'https://www.facebook.com/mnomodesign/', 'Mnomo');\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mnomo</a> 所设计的产品。Dog Den 的床架为橡木制，床垫使用了杜邦面料（Cordura），不会吸收液体或者气味，非常适合宠物犬使用。小床整体设计新颖，放在家中也能很好地融入环境，不会显得突兀。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181709R64sijIlQowE5Hte.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817093KejQuBIbmOfLNhp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181710dKCi7tBXF2468TMo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181710C3SOf4PokY7tNIKg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Dargett Brewery by Braind</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这是 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://braind.am/\">Braind</a> 为亚美尼亚共和国首都埃里温（Yerevan）的 Dargett Brewery 精酿啤酒所设计的包装。Logo 的灵感来源于公元六世纪前的巴比伦地图，圆环所代表的 Bitter River 与品牌名结合，和极具标识性的图案一起巧妙地传递出酿酒传统与工艺仍在延续的概念，复古又清新，让人眼前一亮。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181711bpD2sNUJmSxlMHYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181711LaYpTdVcG31jxAUf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817129OSikglQXjT16JqV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181712xa9hY0vZLfdmF7lN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181713e5xjmgy7EHR0ot81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}